there was a little girl who lived in a village near the forest.  Every day she went to play in the forest, and every day she saw a wolf, but she never got very frightened because the wolf never ate anybody.  She thought the wolf was very ugly and she was also a little bit lazy.  She did not want to do anything about it.

One day her mother said, "Do not go into the house if you hear a wolf outside."

